name: Version 2.4.1
body: - Fixes disabled next button when using arrow numbering

name: Version 2.2.0
body:
* Standard rounds
* Imperial measurement
* Much more target faces (incl. 3D, NFAA, IFAA, ...)
* New arrow positioning with fullscreen zoom
* Support for arrow numbering
* Grouping of trainings per month
* Rounds and passes are shown in one combined view
* Keyboard input mode

Added translations into:
* Catalan
* Chinese
* Hebrew
* Hungarian
* Portuguese
* Slovenian
* Turkish

name: Version 2.0.7

- Fixed number of passes selectable

name: Version 1.9.0
